### Welcome to my GitHub Page!

Here are my projects:

##[Betting Simulator](http://z3ntu.github.io/BettingSimulator)
BettingSimulator is a Java project done by @lukas8971, @Vynd and me (@z3ntu). It should be / is a desktop application (GUI is JavaFX) for betting on randomly generated football matches. It was done as a school project for the subject "POS1".


##[CS:GO World](http://z3ntu.github.io/csgoworld)
CSGOWORLD is a web project done by @Stollengrollen and me (@z3ntu). It should be / is a website for trading in-game items from Counter Strike: Global Offensive. It was done as a school project for the subject "TINF". You can see it at http://csgoworld.me
